    "course_title": "BIOLOGICAL FACTORS INFLUENCING EXERCISE PERFORMANCE",
    "description": "Explore the physiological, biochemical, and molecular mechanisms of the body's response to both acute and chronic exercise. Examine the body's physiological responses to environmental stressors such as heat, cold, and hypoxia. Gain an in-depth understanding of advanced exercise physiology concepts through the analysis of research publications.",
